===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|spithre|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|spider|spīder|lang=ang}}, {{term|spiþra|spīþra|spider|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|spinþrēn|spider", literally, "spinner|lang=en}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|spend-||pend-||spen-||pen-|to pull, stretch, spin|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|spin||spider|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{term|Spinne||spider|lang=de}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|spinder||spinner, spider|lang=da}}, {{etyl|no|-}} {{term|spider||spider|lang=no}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|spindel||spider|lang=sv}}. More at {{l|en|spin}}.

